  "instructions": [
    "Slice the apples and lardons into thin strips.",
    "Heat a pan over medium heat and add the lardons, cooking until crispy.",
    "Add the gochujang, gochugaru, brown sugar, ginger, and garlic to the pan, stirring to combine.",
    "Add the sliced apples to the pan and cook for 2-3 minutes, until slightly tender.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a salt block and garnish with chopped green onions.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
  ],
